commitResults.messageTitle: Update Delete Command to multiple delete
commitResults.messageBody:
Delete Command only allows user to delete one person.

A delete command that allows multiple index is more user-friendly
because users do not have to type the delete command multiple times.

Let's,
* update the delete command to handle multiple index
* add a few test for multiple delete command
* update the user guide to new delete format
